Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達利安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 經常穿著奇怪的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於連鬍子都長出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能啊 是粘上去的假鬍子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假~胡~子~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 還蠻適合你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的話送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話給個像樣的見面禮怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修伊 傻愣在那裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去備茶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是

